main event: A civilian observed a UFO sighting for 2 seconds on 15 April 1966 in Superior, Wisconsin.
interesting points: The sighting lasted only 2 seconds,The observer reported seeing one object making a downward course,The observation was made with the naked eye,The conclusion of the sighting was identified as an asteroid (meteor),Weather conditions at the time were clear with calm winds.
sighted object: one object resembling a golf ball, white in color
